                <h2>Mobile App</h2>
                <p style="text-align: justify;">School Management Softwares are a mandatory requirement these days in Schools. Browser or Web based School Software solutions which can run on Cloud Model ie. internet are easy to implement and use. a1pathshala.com is a integrated web-based Transaction Platform for Schools and colleges which comes with modules like Student Admission Management, Timetable Management, Library Management, Attendance Management, Employee attendance and recuirtment Management, School Exam Mark sheets and Results Management, Homework Assignment Management etc. A1pathshala.com also provides advanced modules like Online attendance, E-Library.

                We provide separate Login facility by giving online Student Login, Employee Staff Login, Parent Login & School Administrator Login. These logins can also be accessed through your Personalized A1pathshala Mobile APP.A1pathshala.com is by far the Top Solution in the market with Best quality and fastest implementation guarantee. We also provide complete integration with Mobile Bulk SMS, E-Mail, and even provide Mobile Apps for Schools integrated with A1pathshala.com.A1pathshala.com is developed on the concepts of an ERP (Enterprise Resource Package) model and covers each and every department of your school.

                We cover the systems followed by HSEB,PABSON,Nepal Board and all other Boards of Education in Nepal.A1pathshala.com is a venture ICT company of Nepal,Grab Infotech Pvt. Ltd. The company has experience and expertise in elementary to higher education sector in Nepal.</p>

